ifa-metaferthikan-31-brefi" class="d-block h-100-lg" title="ΠΟΥ: «Ζώνη θανάτου» το νοσοκομείο αλ Σίφα- Μεταφέρθηκαν 31 βρέφη"><div class="d-block aspect aspect-sm-1 aspect-lg-114">   <picture> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/megastories_default_desktop/public/articles/2023-11-19/mwra.png?h=a380d568&amp;itok=R_mRly_z 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/megastories_default_desktop_420x470_x2/public/articles/2023-11-19/mwra.png?h=a380d568&amp;itok=YxY9zhp0 2x" media="all and (min-width: 1000px)" type="image/png" /> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/megastories_default_desktop/public/articles/2023-11-19/mwra.png?h=a380d568&amp;itok=R_mRly_z 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/megastories_default_desktop_420x470_x2/public/articles/2023-11-19/mwra.png?h=a380d568&amp;itok=YxY9zhp0 2x" media="all and (min-width: 576px)" type="image/png" /> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/square_medium/public/articles/2023-11-19/mwra.png?h=a380d568&amp;itok=8709d9ei 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/vertical_mobile_fullscreen_424x450_x2/public/articles/2023-11-19/mwra.png?h=a380d568&amp;itok=Haix6zt3 2x" media="all and (min-width: 380px)" type="image/png" /> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/square_medium/public/articles/2023-11-19/mwra.png?h=a380d568&amp;itok=8709d9ei 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/square_big/public/articles/2023-11-19/mwra.png?h=a380d568&amp;itok=ipmLHCQg 2x" media="all" type="image/png" /> <img class=" img-fluid" src="/sites/default/files/styles/square_medium/public/articles/2023-11-19/mwra.png?h=a380d568&amp;itok=8709d9ei" width="450" height="450" alt="Πόλεμος Ισραήλ-Χαμάς: " loading="lazy" /> </picture> </div> </a> <header class="position-absolute px-6 py-6"> <a href="/now/world/poy-zoni-thanatoy-nosokomeio-al-sifa-metaferthikan-31-brefi" class="d-block" title="ΠΟΥ: «Ζώνη θανάτου» το νοσοκομείο αλ Σίφα- Μεταφέρθηκαν 31 βρέφη"><h3 class="m-0 p-0 fedramedium fs-17-v lh-22-v lh-23-v-lg fs-18-v-lg whiteText whiteHover px-4 px-lg-0"> <span 