ημος» που σκηνοθετεί ο Γιώργος Κουτλής.</div></div> <a class="absolute-link" title="Η ασχήμια πρέπει να πεθάνει" href="/culture/theatro/i-ashimia-prepei-na-pethanei"></a> </article></div><div class="divider thinnest d-none d-lg-block showhide-content"></div><div class="container-fluid showhide-content py-2 px-lg-4"><div class="row py-4 px-lg-2"><div class="col-12 col-lg rightdots px-20-v px-lg-4"> <article class="h-100"> <a href="/culture/music/o-antonis-palaskas-einai-o-antonis-pi-apo-ta-90s-tis-ellinikis-electronica" class="d-flex flex-column h-100 justify-content-start" title="Ο Αντώνης Παλάσκας ήταν ο Αντώνης Πι – το τρίτο μέλος των Στέρεο Νόβα"><div class="m-0 p-0 fedranormal lh-rel-1-v fs-4-v mb-3 d-none d-lg-block nohover"> ΜΟΥΣΙΚΗ</div><div class="d-block aspect aspect-16_9">   <picture> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_md_160x90/public/articles/2023-11-19/antonis_20p_20_2821_29%202.jpg?h=9081e4e1&amp;itok=RfLADeY- 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_md_160x90_2x/public/articles/2023-11-19/antonis_20p_20_2821_29%202.jpg?h=9081e4e1&amp;itok=wWfKEWRE 2x, /sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_md_160x90_3x/public/articles/2023-11-19/antonis_20p_20_2821_29%202.jpg?h=9081e4e1&amp;itok=ir8wuCpH 3x" media="all and (min-width: 1000px)" type="image/jpeg" /> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_xl_539x304/public/articles/2023-11-19/antonis_20p_20_2821_29%202.jpg?h=9081e4e1&amp;itok=DRc1pZwl 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_xl_539x304_x2/public/articles/2023-11-19/antonis_20p_20_2821_29%202.jpg?h=9081e4e1&amp;itok=6l93HTv9 2x" media="all and (min-width: 380px)" type="image/jpeg" /> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_lg_330x186/public/articles/2023-11-19/antonis_20p_20_2821_29%202.jpg?h=9081e4e1&amp;itok=wxPMilit 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_lg_330x186_x2/public/articles/2023-11-19/antonis_20p_20_2821_29%202.jpg?h=9081e4e1&amp;itok=2OILWwkv 2x" media="all" type="image/jpeg"