riakos-kynigopoylos-ti-allaxa-sta-krasia-tis-boyrgoyndias" class="d-flex flex-column h-100 justify-content-start" title="Κυριάκος Κυνηγόπουλος: Τι άλλαξα στα κρασιά της Βουργουνδίας"><div class="m-0 p-0 fedranormal lh-rel-1-v fs-4-v mb-3 d-none d-lg-block nohover"> ΤΟ ΚΡΑΣΙ ΜΕ ΑΠΛΑ ΛΟΓΙΑ</div><div class="d-block aspect aspect-16_9">   <picture> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_md_160x90/public/articles/2023-11-16/KRASI_PODCAST_3_0.jpg?h=22290d2f&amp;itok=cvQlha7B 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_md_160x90_2x/public/articles/2023-11-16/KRASI_PODCAST_3_0.jpg?h=22290d2f&amp;itok=vGcNmLrh 2x, /sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_md_160x90_3x/public/articles/2023-11-16/KRASI_PODCAST_3_0.jpg?h=22290d2f&amp;itok=dxnDbcde 3x" media="all and (min-width: 1000px)" type="image/jpeg" /> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_xl_539x304/public/articles/2023-11-16/KRASI_PODCAST_3_0.jpg?h=22290d2f&amp;itok=xG3FaLQH 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_xl_539x304_x2/public/articles/2023-11-16/KRASI_PODCAST_3_0.jpg?h=22290d2f&amp;itok=UZ5yYK0Y 2x" media="all and (min-width: 380px)" type="image/jpeg" /> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_lg_330x186/public/articles/2023-11-16/KRASI_PODCAST_3_0.jpg?h=22290d2f&amp;itok=UwQ3-KBS 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_lg_330x186_x2/public/articles/2023-11-16/KRASI_PODCAST_3_0.jpg?h=22290d2f&amp;itok=UwGy4YzX 2x" media="all" type="image/jpeg" /> <img class=" img-fluid" src="/sites/default/files/styles/aspect_16_9_lg_330x186/public/articles/2023-11-16/KRASI_PODCAST_3_0.jpg?h=22290d2f&amp;itok=UwQ3-KBS" width="330" height="186" alt="krasi" loading="lazy" /> </picture> </div> <header><h3 class="m-0 p-0 fedramedium fs-14-v lh-17-v fedrabook-lg fs-8-v-lg lh-12-v-lg mt-4 mt-lg-3"> Κυριάκος Κυνηγόπουλος: Τι άλλαξα στα κρασιά της Βουργουνδίας</h3> </header> <summary class="m-0 p-0 darkGrayText fedranormal fs-8-v lh-14-v font-italic mt-3 my-lg-0 d-block d-lg-none 