 της Θεσσαλονίκης " loading="lazy" /> </picture> </div></div><div class="position-relative common-block-counter pl-lg-5 pl-17-v-lg col-8 col-lg-12 p-0 pl-3 pt-lg-3 lh-rel-1-v"><div class="m-0 p-0 fedranormal lh-12-v fs-4-v ls-supernarrow d-none d-lg-inline redText"> ΘΕΣΣΑΛΟΝΙΚΗ</div> <span class="m-0 p-0 fedranormal fs-9-v fs-8-v-lg lh-13-v lh-12-v-lg d-lg-none darkGrayText slash"> Θεσσαλονίκη </span><h3 class="m-0 p-0 fedranormal fs-9-v fs-8-v-lg lh-13-v lh-12-v-lg d-inline d-lg-block "> Από το Τοστ Σπέσιαλ του κυρίου Βαγγέλη έχουν περάσει πρωθυπουργοί, αθλητές και ηθοποιοί</h3></div><div class="col-12 p-0 divider thinnest light d-block d-lg-none my-4"></div> </header> </a></article></div><div class="col-12 col-lg-3 rightdots pb-lg-5 px-lg-4"> <article class="h-100"> <a href="https://www.lifo.gr/tropos-zois/gefsi/den-mporeis-na-fantasteis-ti-esti-domna-den-ziseis-mia-bradia-stin-ano-poli" class="d-block" title="Δεν μπορείς να φανταστείς τι εστί Δόμνα, αν δεν ζήσεις μια βραδιά στην Άνω Πόλη"> <header class="row no-gutters px-4 px-lg-0"><div class="col-4 col-lg-12 p-0"><div class="aspect aspect-3_2">   <picture> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/aspect_3_2_md_190x127/public/articles/2023-11-19/domna_20_284_29.jpg?h=7562e635&amp;itok=V3RGFT4C 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/aspect_3_2_md_198x132_x2/public/articles/2023-11-19/domna_20_284_29.jpg?h=7562e635&amp;itok=ieIF4Ytk 2x" media="all and (min-width: 1000px)" type="image/jpeg" /> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/aspect_3_2_sm_152x168/public/articles/2023-11-19/domna_20_284_29.jpg?h=7562e635&amp;itok=Xe14qXhO 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/aspect_3_2_sm_152x102_x2/public/articles/2023-11-19/domna_20_284_29.jpg?h=7562e635&amp;itok=kg_NfCO4 2x" media="all" type="image/jpeg" /> <img class=" img-fluid" src="/sites/default/files/styles/aspect_3_2_md_190x127/public/articles/2023-11-19/domna_20_284_29.jpg?h=7562e635&amp;itok=V3RGFT4C" width="198" height="132" alt="Δεν μπορείς να φανταστείς τι εστί Δόμ